{
  "stem": "7238.4",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "From my brother-in-law, who survived in a hospital in Buchenwald.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They didn't have time to take him with them, and he told me.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we were going further to look.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe in another camp there would be a list.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Until we came to Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] In Frankfurt, one of the rabbis from the United States was preparing-- Rabbi Neuhaus-- a list of survivors.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to this same place came my husband, who is now my husband, but at this time, he was from Czestochowa, and I knew him.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What did he do before he came to Frankfurt?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He also is a survivor of the Holocaust-- however, in a different way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He went under a false name of Wladystaw Pikuba.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He went as a Pole to a factory in Austria, located in Bregenz am Boldensee.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is close to the Swiss border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And they made the-- bouillons were produced over there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was a Pole.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Nobody knew that he was a Jew, because he would not survive.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he had a hard time.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He could not go take a bath.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He could not reveal anything from what happened before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was like one of them, and came Christmas, he was sitting at the head of the table and making all the preparations for the holiday, as if he is one of them.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had a very hard time there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He worked in the factory, and one day, somebody came in and looked behind the heads and figured out, this head looks like a Jewish head.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But he only laughed at what remarks they were making.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Until one day, another Pole who worked with him, cleaning out the big, big pots that they made the [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said, 'You a Jew!'",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
